        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1060",
        "content": "Suddenly something happens; he stops under a tree and waits as for a voice calling his name. Ghosts of old things creep into his consciousness; the voices outside of himself whisper a message concerning the limitations of life.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
