        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1060",
        "content": "During the day she sat in the grand stand with a young man, one of the instructors from the college, who was a guest of her mother's.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
