        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1060",
        "content": "While they sat together in the grand stand and while the eyes of former schoolmates were upon them, she paid so much attention to her escort that he grew interested.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
